headline.main: Canada Today: Border Anxiety, Homelessness and Prehistoric Life

lead_paragraph: Sore ribs or sore stomach, it doesn't seem to matter to Rory McIlroy. After being gone for seven weeks, he took a two-shot lead into the weekend at the Mexico Championship with a chance to return to No. 1 in the world.
